HasDirectionsRenderer Renders directions retrieved in the form of a DirectionsResult object retrieved from the DirectionsService.

HasDirectionsRequest A directions query to be sent to the DirectionsService.
HasDirectionsResult The directions response retrieved from the directions server.
HasDirectionsRoute A single route containing a set of legs in JSON format in a DirectionsResult.
HasDirectionsService A service for computing directions between two or more places.
HasDirectionsStatus The status returned by the DirectionsService on the completion of a call to route().
HasDirectionsStep A single DirectionsStep in a DirectionsResult.
HasDirectionsTravelMode The valid travel modes that can be specified in a DirectionsRequest as well as the travel modes returned in a DirectionsStep.
HasDirectionsUnitSystem The valid unit systems that can be specified in a DirectionsRequest.
HasDirectionsWaypoint A DirectionsWaypoint represents a location between origin and destination through which the trip should be routed.
